\c 4
\p
\v 1 Nokuti tarirai, rinouya zuva rinopisa sechoto; zvino vese vanozvikudza, hongu vese vanoita zvakaipa vachava mashanga, uye zuva rinouya richavapisa, anoreva Jehovha wehondo, zvekuti haringavasiiri mudzi kana davi.
\p
\v 2 Asi kwamuri munotya zita rangu, zuva rekururama richabuda nekuporesa pamapapiro aro. Uye richabuda, zvino muchabuda mugouruka semhuru muchirugu.
\v 3 Muchatsikira vakaipa pasi, nokuti vachava madota pasi pezvitsiko zvetsoka dzenyu nezuva randicha\add zvi\add*ita, anoreva Jehovha wehondo.
\p
\v 4 Rangarirai murairo waMozisi muranda wangu, wandakamuraira paHorebhu, waIsraeri wese, mitemo nemitongo.
\p
\v 5 Tarirai, ndichakutumirai Eria muporofita, kutangira kuuya kwezuva guru rinotyisa raJehovha.
